HEADWORD: manila bay
<hw>manila bay</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The name of a naval battle in the
Spanish-American War (1898), in which the American fleet under
<person>Admiral Dewey</person> defeated the Spanish fleet off the shore
of Manila in the Philippines.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

